lead_paragraph: Hillary Rodham Clinton voiced support Friday for President Barack Obama's use of executive actions to protect about 5 million immigrants from deportation, setting up a sharp contrast with Republicans on an issue that could play a leading role in the next presidential campaign.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Backs Obama Immigration Move
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton Backs Obama Immigration Move
